    <string name="about1">Zazen Meditation Timer — Sa\'aatii xiinxala salphaa kutaalee adda ta\'an, sagalee bilbilaa fi bulchiinsa turtii qabu.</string>
    <string name="about2">Jalqaba kan uume Stefan Gaffga dha. Yeroo ammaa kan kunuunsu Georg Graf.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Wiinfried kan &lt;a href="http://www.meditationsuhren.de">http://www.meditationsuhren.de&lt;/a&gt; Sagaleewwan Bell guddaa akkasii waan nuuf dhiheesseef galatoomaa!</string>
    <string name="about3">&lt;a href="https://github.com/georgernstgraf/zazentimer/issues">Dhimmoota GitHub irratti gabaasuu&lt;/a&gt;</string>
